>
> =C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0In Massachusetts the right wing base was in=
fused with excitement over
> the possibility of taking progressive icon Ted Kennedy=E2=80=99s Senate s=
eat =E2=80=93 and
> hobbling Obama=E2=80=99s agenda in the Senate. =C2=A0The Democratic base =
was not inspired
> by the relatively bland Coakley and has been generally dispirited by the
