> battles =E2=80=93 to defend the status quo.
>
> =C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0Though I don=E2=80=99t believe that the sha=
pe of the health care bill would
> have likely been a great deal different, there is no question that Presid=
ent
> Obama would be in better political shape with the base of the Democratic
> Party if he had been a more forceful advocate of the public option =E2=80=
=93 and
